<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="attack-n">attack <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'tæk/    美 /ə'tæk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 攻击；进攻：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>air attack</strong> 
空袭</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>make fierce <strong>attacks</strong> against / <strong>on</strong> 
对…发动猛烈袭击</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When a plant is <strong>under attack</strong>, it sends out certain chemicals.
当植物遭受侵害时，会释放出某些化学物质。</p><footer>2017 全国改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 抨击：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a personal attack 
人身攻击</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] (疾病等) 侵袭；发作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He suffered <strong>a heart attack</strong>.
他心脏病发作了。</p></div></div>